  <brief_title>Comparison of Blood Loss in Laparoscopic vs Open Pancreaticoduodenectomy in Patients With Periampullary Carcinoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Blood Loss in Laparoscopic vs Open Pancreaticoduodenectomy in Patients With Periampullary Carcinoma - A Randomized Clinical Trial</official_title>
