  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      the study is designed to compare the blood loss between laparoscopic vs open
      pancreaticoduodenectomy in a randomized clinical trial
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      the study will assess the difference in the amount of blood loss in Lap vs Open WPD. the
      amount of blood loss will be calculated on the basis of a formula which takes pre operative
      and post operative hematocrit, PCV and blood volume into consideration.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
